Stephen L. WARDIN, Claimant-Appellant, v. Anthony J. PRINCIPI, Secretary of Veterans Affairs, Respondent-Appellee. No. 04-7150. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Oct. 20, 2004.

ON MOTION

ORDER

Upon consideration of Stephen L. War-din’s unopposed motion to voluntarily dismiss his appeal,

IT IS ORDERED THAT:

(1) The motion is granted.

(2) Each side shall bear its own costs.
